imdb.plot outline: Lydia Nicole brings common sense to the forefront of sabor picante with her "Common Sense Mamita" Vlogs. The Veteran actress and comedienne gives weekly advice on being more common sense savvy. Her experience and humor makes each episode spicy and delicious.
